article_title: Lightning Round: 3D Systems, Union Pacific & More
article_text: Are you ready skeedaddy???!!! It’s time for the Lightning Round.  Cramer makes the call on viewer favorites.  3D Systems (DDD): In the space I  like Stratasys better, said Cramer.  Union Pacific (UNP):  I wouldn’t own the stock north of  $160, said Cramer.
